data.description: Welcome to this extraordinary 4 bedroom 2.5 bathroom home that also offers additional 1200 square-foot unfinished basement providing limitless possibilities. Great layout and view with all the privacy and amenities you could want in a growing area, and only 30 minutes to downtown Savannah. The HVAC system has been replaced with, a top-of-the-line, Bryant Evolution series - with 3 zones to ensure optimal comfort, new roof, new septic, new trex deck overlooking a beautiful stocked pond offering endless outdoor opportunities and relaxation. You will also find a 150-yard shooting range & a 50-yard archery range to ensure all your recreational needs are met. Additional amenities include a storage building with electricity, second septic with 200 amp service and countless other upgrades throughout, creating an exceptional living experience. The land at 128 Buford Hill Rd does convey with the purchase and the 2023 manufactured ranch style home will be moved unless purchased separately.
